§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ A ❬cone❭ is a subset of $n$-dimensional space which is
    closed under positive scalar multiplication. ⦉

  ‖ A ❬halfline❭ or ❬ray❭ is a point and all positive scalar
    multiples of that point. ⦉

  ‖ A cone is a union of halflines. ⦉

  ‖ The origin may or may not be included. ⦉
